block.original:
“Þria vissak elda,þria vissak arna;

vask þrimr verumvegin at hūsi;

einn vǫrumk Sigurþrǫllum betri,

es brø̄þr mīnirat bana urþu.

block.translation:
The brave boys I summonedto secret speech;

For my woes requitalI might not win

Till off the headsof the Hniflungs I hewed.

